{"parse":{"title":"Oily Blackmouth","pageid":15669,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_MonsterHead_04\n|stack=20\n|name=Oily Blackmouth\n|quality=Common\n|vendor={{cost||15}}\n|sell={{cost|||4}}\n|ilvl=15\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n\n'''Oily Blackmouth''' is obtained by [[fishing]] and is a component in [[Blackmouth Oil]] (made with [[Alchemy]]). Fishing for Oily Blackmouth requires [[Fishing_locations#Fishing_skill_levels_by_zone|(third tier)]] fishing skill-level of 55 (or 150 to ensure a catch) . Oily Blackmouth can be fished straight from the water or also from an Oily Blackmouth [[Fishing#Schools_of_Fish|School]]. \n\n== Oily Blackmouth as an ingredient ==\n\n=== Alchemy ===\n*[[Blackmouth Oil]]\n\n==Farming Locations==\n\n;{{Alliance Icon Small}} Alliance:\n:* The docks at [[Menethil Harbor]] in [[Wetlands]].\n:* The docks at [[Booty Bay]] and along the southeast shore of [[Stranglethorn Vale]].\n:* The western coast of mainland [[Feralas]].\n:* The northeastern coast of [[Tanaris]] near [[Steamwheedle Port]].\n:* The coast of [[Darkshore]].\n:* The coast of [[Westfall]], look for schools.\n:* The docks and coastal shoreline of [[Southshore]] in the [[Hillsbrad Foothills]].\n:* The small lake South West of [[Blood Watch]] on [[Bloodmyst Isle]].\n:* The dock to [[Auberdine]] in [[Stormwind Harbor]].\n\n;{{Horde Icon Small}} Horde:\n:* The docks around [[Ratchet]] in the Barrens. Can get with fishing level 10 and shiny bauble.\n:* The coastline at [[Zoram'Gar]] in [[Ashenvale]].\n:* The coastline of [[Silverpine Forest]].\n:* The docks at [[Booty Bay]] south of Stranglethorn Vale.\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|6358}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/oily_blackmouth.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n== ==\n*[[Places_to_Farm#Oily_Blackmouth|Click here for places to farm Oily Blackmouth]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft alchemy ingredient items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:Alchemy Materials]]"}}}